#  Aura Quest Generator.
Heavily under construction.
Simple java app to generate Quest scripts based on simple templates. Built for Project Aura.
You can check the original forum thread [here](http://aura-project.org/forum/topic/215-quest-generator/).

## Authors and Contributors
@YaibaToKen
@exectails

## Changelog
### 23/03/2016:

    Finished the core for the app:

        Base classes have been finished;

        Pushing Script Object instance into file has been done;

        Utility class has been created;

        Interfaces defined for Reward, Objective and Prerequisite types;


    Started work on the User Interface:

        Basic layout using JFrame;

        Initial idea on how to pull and from interface to Object instances;


    Started work on the Reward types:

        Base interface has been established;

        Missing Skill, Skill training and Stat bonus;


    Started work on the Objective types:

        Base interface has been established;

        Kill objective has been implemented;


    Started work on the Prerequisites types:

        Base interface has been established;
